---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Support Ancient Philosophia"
  description="Ancient Philosophia is a free, open-source educational website. If you find it useful, you can help keep it running by buying a coffee — it's entirely voluntary and deeply appreciated."
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-10">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-[var(--color-fg-primary)] mb-3">
        Support This Project
      </h1>
      <p class="text-[var(--color-fg-secondary)] text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Ancient Philosophia is and will always be free to use.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main card -->
    <div class="bg-[var(--color-bg-card)] rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-bg-tertiary)] p-8 mb-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
        <span class="text-2xl" aria-hidden="true">☕</span>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-[var(--color-gold-leaf)]">
          Buy me a coffee
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-[var(--color-fg-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Running a website has modest but real costs: domain registration, DNS, CDN hosting, and
          the occasional database or compute resource as the site grows. Every euro or dollar goes
          directly toward keeping the lights on and the content improving.
        </p>
        <p>
          This site is a solo passion project &mdash; researched, written, and maintained by one
          person who believes that ancient history and language learning should be freely accessible
          to everyone, not locked behind paywalls.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you've found Ancient Philosophia genuinely useful &mdash; whether you used it to study
          for a course, satisfy a curiosity, or just fell down an enjoyable rabbit hole of ancient
          civilizations &mdash; a small contribution is a wonderful way to say thank you.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-fg-muted)] text-sm">
          Contributions are entirely voluntary. There are no premium features, no membership tiers,
          and no expectation of payment. The site will remain open and free regardless.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Ko-fi button -->
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a
          href="https://ko-fi.com/jameschien"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold text-white transition-opacity hover:opacity-90"
          style="background-color: #f45d22;"
        >
          <span>☕</span>
          Support on Ko-fi
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Other ways to help -->
    <div class="bg-[var(--color-bg-card)] rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-bg-tertiary)] p-6">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--color-gold-leaf)] mb-4">
        Other ways to help
      </h2>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-[var(--color-fg-secondary)] text-sm leading-relaxed">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="text-[var(--color-bronze-light)] mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>
          <span>
            <strong class="text-[var(--color-fg-primary)]">Contribute content</strong> &mdash;
            open a pull request on{' '}
            <a
              href="https://github.com/shc261392/ancient-philosophia"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="text-[var(--color-link)] hover:underline"
            >
              GitHub
            </a>{' '}
            to add or improve civilizations, languages, or resources.
          </span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="text-[var(--color-bronze-light)] mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>
          <span>
            <strong class="text-[var(--color-fg-primary)]">Spread the word</strong> &mdash; share
            a page with a student, a colleague, or anyone curious about ancient history.
          </span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span class="text-[var(--color-bronze-light)] mt-0.5 shrink-0">→</span>
          <span>
            <strong class="text-[var(--color-fg-primary)]">Report errors</strong> &mdash; if you
            spot something inaccurate, please{' '}
            <a
              href="mailto:support@ancient-philosophia.org"
              class="text-[var(--color-link)] hover:underline"
            >
              let us know
            </a>. Good scholarship matters.
          </span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<!-- Ko-fi floating widget (support page only) -->
<script is:inline src="https://storage.ko-fi.com/cdn/scripts/overlay-widget.js"></script>
<script is:inline>
  kofiWidgetOverlay.draw('jameschien', {
    'type': 'floating-chat',
    'floating-chat.donateButton.text': 'Support me',
    'floating-chat.donateButton.background-color': '#f45d22',
    'floating-chat.donateButton.text-color': '#fff'
  });
</script>
